{
  "text": "A 20-year-old Asian Indian female presented to our Oral and Maxillofacial unit with a lump on the left side of her forehead. The lump has been present for 1 month, and she had developed a psychological complex due to the unaesthetic appearance. The lesion was initially 1\u00d71 cm [CITATION_1] and had eventually progressed to the presentation size over the month.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "58480073"
